# smoke test: test "name" panics block syntax (ADR 0013 + ADR 0012)
#
# Verifies that test "name" panics ... end blocks:
#   - desugar to test_panics__<sanitized> function names
#   - PASS when the body calls panic() (exit 101 + __TYRA_PANIC__ sentinel)
#   - FAIL when the body exits normally (no panic) — but we don't test that
#     failure path here; it's covered by panic_expect_smoke_test.tyra
#
# test_panics__named_intentional_panic must PASS.
# test__named_no_panic must PASS (plain test alongside panics test).

test "named intentional panic" panics
  panic("intentional boom for named panics block")
end

test "named no panic"
  Ok(())
end
